content.xhtml:p: This Block is the Bool Inputs for the Raw Materials (which are accepted)
This Block is the Bool Inputs for the Base Materials (which are Rejected)
If Blue Raw or Blue Bad materials are detected, Engage Pivot Arm 0.
If Metal Raw or Metal Bad materials are detected, Engage Pivot Arm 1.
If the Blue Base is detected by vision sensor 1, turn on pusher 0.
If the Metal Base is detected by vision sensor 2, turn on pusher 1.
For the Green Lids, Have PnP move Z-axis toward conveyor. Then grab and move x and deposit the lids into the bin. Diffuse sensors increment good count.

If the Machine Centers are Busy, and there is not a product breaking the retro reflectors at the end of the 2m out conveyors, then turn on the conveyor belt to position lids for pick up by the PnP robots.
Deploy Stopper Blade if diffuse 3 goes high to position lid under PnP0.
